txt.en: The ring is dull, and the design feels ancient. You cannot discern anything else about it. You should show it to one of the Rangers at the colossus camp.
'You found this within a crawler, you say? I wonder how it got there....'
You found a dull ancient ring within the remains of crawler. A Ranger at the colossus would be interested in seeing this.
Find a Ranger at the colossus camp to speak with about the ring you found
The colossus camp is north of the Barandalf.\n\nOne of the Rangers at the colossus camp may be interested in seeing the ring you have found.
